formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1)This certificate is being issued on request of M/S. Friends Developer for RERA
compliance of Project EVOQ and it is based on the  books of accounts as on 30.06.2023 maintained by the firm and
other records/documents produced before us for our verification and information & explanations provided to us by the partners of
the firm and to the best of our knowledge and belief. Also the estimated figures wherever provided herein above are taken as
certified by the Engineer/Architect and Partner of the firm.
2) Further, the details provided in the Annexure to this certificate, i.e. calculation of receivables from sales of sold inventory (flats),
booking of garages and parkings and valuation of unsold inventory and other details is based on management representation
provided to us.
3) As per information & explanations provided to us by the partners of the firm this is to inform you that unsecured loans taken
from lendors are used for marketing purpose not for construction purpose . Hence interest paid on unsecured loans, if any, not considered in total cost incurred and paid.
.
4) During our verification of books of accounts for the period of this certificate, we found that at various instances collection received from buyer has been deposited in
current account of promotor instead RERA account , Whereas as per RERA regulation once project is registered with RERA authority then 70% of the balance receivables of ongoing projects will have to be deposited in designated ( RERA ) account. This is in contravention of provisions of Rera Act,2016.
